  "response": "Several online shopping sites are popular in India for purchasing bags. The \"best\" site can depend on various factors such as product range, pricing, customer service, and delivery options. Some of the top online shopping sites for bags in India are:\n\n1. **Amazon India**: Extensive variety, competitive prices, and reliable delivery.\n2. **Flipkart**: Wide range of brands and styles, regular sales, and discounts.\n3. **Myntra**: Known for fashion products, including a vast collection of bags.\n4. **Limeroad**: Specializes in fashion accessories, including a trendy collection of bags.\n5. **Ajio**: Fashion-forward options and regular discounts.\n6. **Tata Cliq**: Offers a good selection of branded bags.\n7. **Nykaa Fashion**: Focuses on fashion and lifestyle products, including bags.\n8. **Bagzone**: Specialized in bags with various styles and brands.\n9. **Voylla**: Offers a collection of stylish and chic bags.\n\nIt's always a good idea to compare prices, read reviews, and check return policies before making a purchase.",
